These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, bartender
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, helicopter
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the lawyer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | filmmaking       | cooking |
| Job         | bartender | lawyer  |
| Sport       | cricket    | lacrosse    |
| Transport   | helicopter       | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, fanta
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, coach
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, family
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the electrician is on the far left##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | juice |
| Job           | electrician | coach      |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | zombie      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | cricket     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, water
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, peas
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, disco
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, bus
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking juice is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | juice | water  |
| Food          | asparagus    | peas   |
| Music-Genre   | disco  | classical   |
| Transport     | bus     | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, water
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, artichoke
The people have 2 different jobs:  social-worker, pilot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, ambient
1. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking water is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | cola       | water |
| Food          | artichoke         | blueberry    |
| Job           | pilot | social-worker    |
| Music-Genre   | classical           | ambient   |

