2 different pets are kept: snake, goat
1. the colombian is the owner of the goat##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | spinach | asparagus |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | r&b      |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian    |
| Pet           | snake    | goat    |

