.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, dancer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: epic, adventure
2 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, roller
1. the bartender is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the bartender is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the owner of the pony is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | dancer | bartender     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic          | adventure |
| Pet           | pony          | hedgehog    |
| Transport     | roller            | motorbike       |

 